<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>A 12-day-old baby boy has died after he was mauled to death by a dog.</p>

<p>South Yorkshire Police rushed to a property in the village of Woodlands in Doncaster on Sunday afternoon following reports that a child had been attacked.</p>

<p>The baby was rushed to hospital with serious injuries but died a short time later.</p>

<p>A man, 35, and woman, 27, have since been arrested on suspicion of gross negligence manslaughter.   </p>
